column1: #lines starting with # should be ignored
#USERNAME should be replaced by the username
#PREVIOUS_POINTS should be replaced by the points the user add before this month
#EARNED_POINTS should be replaced by the points the user earned this month
#DISCOUNTED_POINTS should be replaced by the points that were converted to euros
#ACTUAL_POINTS should be replaced by the points the user will have for the next month
#MONTH_CHARGED_VALUE should be replaced by the total of euros to charge the user for this month
#List of charges
#vehicle description - a descriptive reference for the vehicle e.g. PT050 or ePT050
#vehicle unlock time and vehicle lock time - should be given in miliseconds
#origin park latitude
column4: destination park longitude- when a vehicle is parked
column5: the park latitude and longitude are given in decimal degrees e.g. 41.152712

column1: #time spent in seconds - total time spent in seconds between vehicle unlock and lock
#charged value - value charges in euros
column2: rounded to two decimal places e.g. 2.456 is shown as 2.46
